des:
Radio Olinda FM 101.3 is a company of the Syria Communications System Ltda. Olinda FM has its studio 01 in Tucunduva - RS and Studio 02 in Horizontina - RS. With 5 kW of power, its coverage area covers the entire Northwest Region of Rio Grande do Sul and Northeast of Argentina. It has an eclectic programming, always bringing Music and Information to its listeners, being a reference as a means of communication in its coverage area. Olinda FM 101.3 - The Radio of Music and Information!
